We should try to maintain a certain pattern when using modal steps and I heavily recommend using this kind of pattern Instead of using just numbers because is more readable: 
```
const STEPS = {
	LIST_ROOMS: 'LIST_ROOMS',
	CONFIRM_DELETE: 'CONFIRM_DELETE',
};
```

